summary: RESEACH FOR A BOOK, PLEASE HELP
body:
RESEACH FOR A BOOK, PLEASE HELP

Hi, I’m looking for Americans. And if you aren’t, please reboot so an American may see it. Or if you happen to know a lot about America schools systems. If you would maybe like to answer these questions it would make my day. Thank you!


1. Which classes/ courses did you take/ are you taking/ are you going to take in Junior year of high school?

2. What is a semester?

3. When do you have vacation? Like how long for 4th of July, Christmas and so on?

4. How often do you have each course/ class?

5. When is homecoming?

6. When do you take SAT’s?

7. When is the football season in high schools?

8. Is it both girls and boys who represent the school in football? If yes, together or apart?

9. Are all sports available year round?

10. Is lunch at the same time for everyone? Does it cost money? If yes, do you pay in the canteen or somewhere else?

summary: why didn’t you include girl group stans in your kpop callout [submission by themodrenman@gmail.com] okay 1. this is very...
caption:
why didn’t you include girl group stans in your kpop callout

[submission by themodrenman@gmail.com]

okay 1. this is very accurate and if u like. meant to call me out for being a marvel blog…. guess what buddy ive written multiple posts criticizing marvel, its fanbase, the mcu’s writers (and also the comics once, iirc), and i recognize that these are all problems! but here’s the thing: purity culture is dead and i can enjoy things while also being critical of them lmao

2. i wrote the original post in like 3 minutes and didn’t expect it to get more than 30 notes, at best, because that’s what most of my original posts get (not counting art, which get, like, 200 notes or something– so still not tons lmao). if you look in the notes i do go more in-depth about girl groups! but also? most people on tumblr “stan” the boy groups more, and that’s why this was predominantly meant for them. (more in-depth explanation can be found, again, in the notes, because i am sick and tired of having to rehash the same arguments again in DMs, replies, and asks)

and like, listen. im not here to pick a fight but seriously what crawled up your ass that you had to be this passive aggressive about this lmao
